<ptxt>Input voltage to ECM remains 0.3 V or less, or 4.7 V or higher for more than 5 seconds, when 2 or more seconds have elapsed after turning engine switch on (IG)</ptxt>
<ptxt>(1 trip detection logic)</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>No VVT sensor signal to ECM during cranking</ptxt>
<ptxt>(1 trip detection logic)</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
